<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Listing Approved — AddressGuru</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f6f7fb; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif; color: #333; }
    .wrapper { width: 100%; padding: 40px 0; background: #f6f7fb; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; background: #fff; margin: auto; border-radius: 14px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); overflow: hidden; }
    .header {   background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e35, #ffb347); text-align: center; padding: 30px 20px; color: #ffffff; }
    .header img { width: 150px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .header h1 { font-size: 22px; margin: 0; font-weight: 600; }
    .content { padding: 30px 25px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .content p { margin: 15px 0; }
    .btn { display: inline-block;   background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e35, #ffb347); color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 25px; transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .btn:hover {   background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e35, #ffb347); box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(34,197,94,0.3); }
    .footer { background: #fafafa; padding: 25px 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #777; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    .footer a { color: #f7941d; text-decoration: none; }
    .footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .content { padding: 20px 15px; }
      .btn { width: 100%; text-align: center; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">
          <img src="https://www.addressguru.in/images/logopng.png" alt="AddressGuru Logo">
        </a>
        <h1>Your Listing is Live</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>
          Great news — your listing <strong>“{{listingTitle}}”</strong> has been approved and is now live!
        </p>
        <p style="text-align:center;">
          <a href="{{listingUrl}}" class="btn" target="_blank">View Listing Now</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} AddressGuru. All rights reserved. <br>
        <a href="https://addressguru.ae" target="_blank">addressguru.ae</a> | <a href="mailto:support@addressguru.ae">support@addressguru.ae</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
